Hive Installation
-----------------


1) Extract the hive tar

tar -zxvf hive-0.12.0

2) Set java,hive and hadoop paths in .bashrc file and execute the .bashrc file

echo $JAVA_HOME  (Check the JAVA PATH)

vi .bashrc

export JAVA_HOME=/home/saravanan/jdk1.6.0_45
export HADOOP_HOME=/home/saravanan/hadoop-1.2.1
export HIVE_HOME=/home/saravanan/hive-0.12.0    

source .bashrc

3) Start hadoop Cluster 

4)cd hive-0.12.0
5)bin/hive
6)show tables;

